1162
01:50:15,243 --> 01:50:16,005
Beneran nih?

1163
01:50:16,110 --> 01:50:17,908
Aku seorang pria yg
memegang kata2nya lho.

1164
01:50:19,580 --> 01:50:20,308
Putrimu cantik nggak tuh?

1165
01:50:20,414 --> 01:50:23,907
Tentu saja dong.

1166
